# PUBLIC MODE (active): daily reports + bets/profit ARE committed to this repo,
# and Vercel auto-deploys on push (no `vercel --prod` needed). To switch back to
# private mode, un-comment the two lines below and deploy via the CLI instead.
# /data/*.json
# /public/reports/*.html

# The repo-root .gitignore carries a Python "lib/" rule (packaging artifacts)
# that would otherwise swallow this Next.js app's own source folder. Re-include
# it so a fresh clone actually has lib/format.ts, lib/types.ts, lib/data.ts.
!/lib/
!/lib/**
